General.Name: M Vest Water A/S
General.Description: M Vest Water AS, an environmental technology company, provides solutions for water and wastewater treatment. The company offers products and solutions for water and sludge treatment. It provides NorwaFloc, a natural and biodegradable combined flocculant/coagulant product; NorwaPol, a polishing process with automatic backflushing; and activated filter media. The company serves oil and gas, aquaculture, sludge dewatering, municipal, and other industries. It primarily operates in Norway, the Middle East, China, Japan, and Malaysia. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Bergen, Norway.
